                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog. Light winds becoming east to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the middle of the day then becoming light in the early afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 6 with daytime temperatures reaching around 16.</text>
