            <forecast-period index="2" start-time-local="2026-06-26T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-27T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-25T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-26T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">The chance of morning fog. Sunny afternoon. Light winds becoming southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the early afternoon then becoming light in the late afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 6 with daytime temperatures reaching around 17.</text>
